<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">-<br>只有两步：<br><br><b>“Write drunk; edit sober.”</b><br><br>（经网友 davida 考证，该句出自 Peter De Vries 笔下：<a href="http://mattwie.be/2011/12/1345/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">mattwie.be/2011/12/1345</span><span class="invisible">/</span><span class="ellipsis"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a>。这个网页下面还有一名同学似乎也独立地发明了它。）<br>-


